    - target: {fileID: 8063609272687953924, guid: 58206228119b2ed4ab0ad31cdc8ed92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'The recommended way to survive is to destroy all enemies before they
        do the same to you.


        Otherwise, things may get difficult.


        To
        help you stay alive, your ship is equipped with powerful shields in addition
        to its base hull.


        Your shield is divided into four sectors. Each
        sector has its own energy, which slowly restores over time.


        Your
        hull, however, does not regenerate. Once your structural integrity is damaged,
        it stays damaged.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8063609272687953924, guid: 58206228119b2ed4ab0ad31cdc8ed92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_fontSize
      value: 22
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8063609272687953924, guid: 58206228119b2ed4ab0ad31cdc8ed92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_fontSizeBase
      value: 22
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
