    - target: {fileID: 8063609272687953924, guid: 58206228119b2ed4ab0ad31cdc8ed92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'To destroy your enemies, your ship is equipped with several types of
        weapons.



        Some weapons are smart and can track targets automatically.
        Others require careful aiming.



        To help with aiming, your turrets
        are equipped with a laser detection system.



        The rule is simple:



        If
        it is red, shoot it.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
